  "detailed_description": "Adrift is a casual single player game about fishing in space. You will sail around the universe fishing for planets, buying upgrades, and customizing your sick crib! Back home you will <strong>Sacrifice</strong> your haul to a black hole for star dust. Star dust allows you to by sweet things like items, and upgrades.",
